korean: 재밌는 영상을 하나 봤는데 연달아 계속 보게 됐다.
추천 영상이 계속 떠서 끊을 수가 없었어.
english: I watched one interesting video and ended up watching continuously.
Recommended videos kept appearing, so I couldn't stop.
I watched until late at night and fell asleep at dawn.
I regret it because I have to wake up early tomorrow.
